{"tid":1676823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尋人 14歲學生哥","createTime":"2019-10-26T16:46:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T18:01:57.000Z","uid":99274,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"561b273de5ad0c3193604030c7e911a0706adafd","tid":1676823,"uid":99274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:46:22.000Z","msg":"尋人<br />\n<br />\nKwong Siu Tim<br />\n5137 16xx<br />\n<br />\n星火話唔確定佢真係比人拉左所以幫唔到<br />\n話要搵到佢屋企人同埋知道邊間狗屋先幫到手<br />\n<br />\n但又唔確定佢比狗拉左<br />\n佢講過搵唔到佢超過12個鐘就當佢比狗拉左<br />\n依家己經差唔多24個鐘<br />\n<br />\n佢只係一個我見過幾面嘅學生<br />\n14歲住秀茂坪<br />\n10月25日晚失聯到依家<br />\n我只得佢全名同手提電話<br />\n如果有識佢嘅朋友可唔可以幫手問下佢屋企人"},{"pid":"0cbf9fd0d1c156219e391b868be3b244af6d43e9","tid":1676823,"uid":99274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:47:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b106f73d8344dd28dc61aff95c75b396ec16b7fa","tid":1676823,"uid":280867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:47:28.000Z","msg":"屌講乜撚嘢五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1676770\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1676770</a>"},{"pid":"fd023b8de40d0ab12ebce6ee4b9347abb534a772","tid":1676823,"uid":224829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:47:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa89ddb57844ced49923f4b493136ffdfdf563cb","tid":1676823,"uid":36658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:48:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1654ffc9ae81aea563ee7fd2c3b3df20c221d2b6","tid":1676823,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:48:43.000Z","msg":"[區議會|選戰]有個傻仔幫近千位候選人分黃藍假獨立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1676724\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1676724</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e25685c12be1e8ac6d33e3429b6189b48b7408","tid":1676823,"uid":99274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re